[DOCUMENT]
TITLE: Tooling

[SECTION]
TITLE: Monitoring

[REQUIREMENT]
UID: TOOL-MON-001
TITLE: Can monitor system performance and health
STATEMENT: The system should be able to monitor its own performance and health, such as CPU usage, memory usage, network usage, and report any issues or errors to a logging system.

[/SECTION]

[SECTION]
TITLE: Reports

[REQUIREMENT]
UID: TOOL-REP-001
TITLE: Can generate reports and statistics on data usage and performance
STATEMENT: The system should be able to generate reports and statistics on data usage and performance to help users optimize their data collection and analysis processes.

[/SECTION]

[SECTION]
TITLE: CLI

[REQUIREMENT]
UID: TOOL-CLI-001
TITLE: Can list plugins from CLI
STATEMENT: Plugins defined in xml files can be fetched and listed so the user knows which ones are available.

[/SECTION]
